# interactionOperationNotSupported

**Type Property**

The [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INInteraction] object could not be donated or deleted because those capabilities are not supported on the current device.

## Declaration

```swift
static var interactionOperationNotSupported: INIntentError.Code { get }
```

## Interaction Errors

- **donatingInteraction**: The [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INInteraction] object could not be donated to the system.
- **deletingAllInteractions**: The system was unable to delete all donated [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INInteraction] objects.
- **deletingInteractionWithIdentifiers**: The system was unable to delete the specified set of [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INInteraction] objects.
- **deletingInteractionWithGroupIdentifier**: The system was unable to delete the [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INInteraction] objects using their group identifier.
